  "instructions": [
    "Preheat grill to medium-high heat.",
    "Cut the tops off the bell peppers and remove seeds.",
    "In a small bowl, mix together feta cheese, kalamata olives, fresh oregano, and garlic.",
    "Stuff each bell pepper with the cheese mixture.",
    "Brush the grill with olive oil to prevent sticking.",
    "Place the bell peppers on the grill and cook for 5 minutes per side.",
    "Transfer the peppers to a baking dish and brush with lemon juice.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Bake in a preheated oven at 375°F for 10 minutes.",
    "Serve warm and enjoy!"
